&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking to thrive in a stimulating work environment ?&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join Levio, a leader in digital transformation, and take your career to the next level. You will work alongside high-caliber professionals on ambitious, large-scale technology projects, directly embedded in our clients’ environments. At Levio, we value expertise, curiosity, and continuous improvement — and we give you the space to grow.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an Alliance Director to help us build sustainable growth. The role will be hybrid, based in Toronto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why&amp;nbsp;Join&amp;nbsp;Levio?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on complex, high impact digital transformation projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with experienced, multidisciplinary teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously develop your technical and professional expertise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy flexibility, autonomy, and a strong people first culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of an organization that values diversity, inclusion, and innovation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role and Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and grow strategic alliances with key partners (e.g., technology vendors, consulting firms, and ecosystem players) to generate qualified pipeline opportunities within Toronto’s financial services sector.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive top-of-funnel business development, including co-selling motions, joint go-to-market strategies, and partner-led demand generation campaigns targeting Tier 1 banks and insurers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, qualify, and progress new revenue opportunities by leveraging partner networks, proactively sourcing leads, and aligning Levio’s capabilities with client transformation priorities (e.g., digital, data, cloud).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and execute account-based partner strategies across major financial institutions in Toronto, coordinating with Levio sales, delivery, and executive stakeholders to maximize win rates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a market connector and relationship leader, maintaining executive-level partner relationships, representing Levio in the ecosystem, and continuously expanding visibility and credibility within the financial services community&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications and&amp;nbsp;Experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of experience in executive leadership, sales, or consulting within Industrial and supply chain domains. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record in partnerships or business development with hyperscalers, SaaS or Fintech businesses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong executive presence with the ability to influence and engage C-Level stakeholders. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge in digital transformation, banking or insurance industries and emerging technologies. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Great negotiation and communication skills. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation (Ontario) &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The salary range provided reflects a&amp;nbsp;good faith&amp;nbsp;estimate based on factors such as experience, technical&amp;nbsp;expertise, location, and relevant certifications. Final compensation will be&amp;nbsp;determined&amp;nbsp;according to the specific circumstances of each candidate.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Estimated salary range:&lt;/strong&gt; $17

&lt;p&gt;Vous souhaitez vous épanouir dans un environnement de travail stimulant ? Joignez-vous au leader en transformation numérique et boostez votre carrière chez Levio. Nous vous proposons une opportunité unique de développer votre savoir-faire au sein d’une équipe de haut calibre. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;La variété des défis proposés par nos clients vous donnera l’occasion de vous dépasser et de maintenir votre expertise au top. Partagez le quotidien de nos clients et soyez un acteur important dans les projets les plus ambitieux en matière de technologies et de solutions logicielles.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
